NOP

NOP

ADDIU A0 R0 20
JAL SleepProcess ; Sleeps for 20 frames
NOP

JAL GetSpaceData ; Pointer to Space Data at V0
LI A0 77

ADDIU V0 V0 8 ; This gets the X pos of the space
LW V1 0(V0) 
MOVE S0 V1 ; Copy to S6

ADDIU V0 V0 8 ; This gets the Y pos of the space
LW V1 0(V0)
MOVE S1 V1 ; Copy to S7

JAL GetPlayerStruct ; Player Struct at V0
LI A0 -1 ; Current Player

LW V1 0x24(V0) ; Load Offset 24 into V1
ADDIU V1 V1 0xC ; Add 0xC to get current player's X Coords
SW S0 0(V1) 

ADDIU V1 V1 8 ; This should load current player's Y Coords
SW S1 0(V1)

ADDIU A0 R0 0x00 ; Assigns Bar Code fade-in
ADDIU A1 R0 30 ; Assigns 25 frames of fade-in
JAL 0x80061FE8 ; Calls Fade-in

; NAME: HB Fix
; GAMES: MP3_USA
; EXECUTION: Direct

ADDIU SP SP -40
SW RA 36(SP)

LUI T1 hi(0x800CD096)
ADDIU T1 T1 lo(0x800CD096) ; Load Star HB RAM Reserved Space Address
LB T0 0(T1) ; Load Value of Address to T0
BNE T0 R0 putStarHBback
NOP
ADDIU T1 T1 1 ; Load Coins HB RAM Reserved Space Address
LB T0 0(T1)
BNE T0 R0 putCoinsHBback
NOP
ADDIU T1 T1 1 ; Load Item HB RAM Reserved Space Address
LB T0 0(T1)
BNE T0 R0 putItemHBback
NOP
J exit
NOP

putStarHBback:
LUI T2 hi(hidden_block_star_space_index)
ADDIU T2 T2 lo(hidden_block_star_space_index)
SB T0 0(T2) ; Store HB back in its address
SB R0 0(T1) ; Remove HB from RAM Reserved Space
J exit
NOP
